  *     <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/windows/desktop/api/winioctl/ni-winioctl-ioctl_disk_reassign_blocks_ex">IOCTL_DISK_REASSIGN_BLOCKS_EX</a> control code 
  *     supports 8-byte LBAs.
  * 
